name: DOGGY COIN
description: Meet Doggy, the beloved dog of Pepe the Frog created by Matt Furie. Originally a charming sidekick in the meme universe, Doggy has inspired a memecoin that’s capturing the crypto community’s imagination. Doggy the dog of the most memeable memecoin in existence called Pepe. Doggy has no tax fees and the liquidity pool is locked forever
